# Plans

## Wiki-P1 Wiki Knowledge Layer — Storage, Multi-Level Directories, Raw Import, and Frontend
**Status:** done
**Tags:** stack:both
**Depends on:** Wiki-G1, Wiki-A1, Wiki-D1

| Phase | Task | Owner | Duration | Dependencies | Status |
|---|---|---|---|---|---|
| Wiki-P17.1 | WikiPage data model + storage in `{project}/wiki/` with _manifest.json | Core | 2 days | Wiki-D1 | Done |
| Wiki-P17.2 | `list_wiki` and `create_wiki_page` tools for agents | Core | 1 day | Wiki-P17.1 | Done |
| Wiki-P17.3 | `update_wiki_page` tool with version tracking | Core | 1 day | Wiki-P17.1 | Done |
| Wiki-P17.4 | Embedding computation: integrate local embedding model or API-based embeddings | Core | 2 days | Wiki-P17.1 | Proposed |
| Wiki-P17.5 | `query_wiki` tool with FAISS vector similarity search (top-K retrieval) | Core | 2 days | Wiki-P17.4 | Proposed |
