| Wiki-P17.7 | Frontend: full-text + semantic search UI for wiki | UI | 2 days | Wiki-P17.5, Wiki-P17.6 | Proposed |
| Wiki-P17.8 | Frontend: markdown editor with live preview for wiki page editing | UI | 2 days | Wiki-P17.6 | Done |
| Wiki-P17.9 | Backend: TreeNode + recursive directory tree builder + path-based CRUD (multi-level slugs) | Core | 2 days | Wiki-P17.1 | Done |
| Wiki-P17.10 | Backend: Raw file API — multipart upload, file serve, delete, mkdir with path traversal protection | Core | 2 days | Wiki-P17.9 | Done |
| Wiki-P17.11 | Frontend: TreeView recursive component + DropZone native HTML5 drag-and-drop upload | UI | 2 days | Wiki-P17.9, Wiki-P17.10 | Done |
| Wiki-P17.12 | Frontend: WikiView overhaul — dual-region sidebar, raw file preview, path-based page creation | UI | 3 days | Wiki-P17.11 | Done |
| Wiki-P17.13 | Integration: agent tools registered per profession, wiki tools in allowed_tools | Core | 1 day | Wiki-P17.2, Wiki-P17.3 | Done |
| Wiki-P17.14 | Integration tests: wiki CRUD, tree navigation, raw upload/download | Core | 2 days | Wiki-P17.13 | Proposed |

